We are committed to ensuring our workplace rewards everyone fairly for their efforts no matter what background,
race or ethnicity, with men and women paid equally for equivalent roles across our business. NewLaw aims to provide
an inclusive workplace and opportunities for all colleagues to develop their full potential.

